vice->shippingservice`: 调用延迟增加。\n\n### 假设分析\n1. **根因组件**: `checkoutservice`\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 显著增加。\n   - **证据**: 内部调用 (`checkoutservice->checkoutservice`) 延迟倍数高达 7.48，表明该服务在处理请求时出现严重性能问题。\n\n2. **次要组件**: `shippingservice`\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 增加。\n   - **证据**: `checkoutservice->shippingservice` 的延迟倍数达到 4.59，可能是由于 `checkoutservice` 的问题导致下游服务超时。\n\n3. **网络或资源瓶颈**:\n   - **原因**: 多个服务的延迟增加。\n   - **证据**: `frontend->frontend` 和 `frontend->checkoutservice` 的延迟增加，可能表明网络或资源瓶颈。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"内部调用延迟从 13,865.84 ms 增加到 103,683.57 ms（倍数: 7.48）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用延迟从 9,415.74 ms 增加到 43,210.44 ms（倍数: 4.59）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n1. **深入检查 `checkoutservice`**:\n   - 检查其资源使用情况（CPU、内存、网络）。\n   - 检查是否有死锁或线程池耗尽问题。\n\n2. **检查 `shippingservice`**:\n   - 确认其是否受到 `checkoutservice` 的影响，或自身是否存在问题。\n\n3. **网络监控**:\n   - 检查节点之间的网络延迟和带宽使用情况。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "6add78b2-480", "component": "paymentservice", "reason": "pod_processes spike (1.0→9.0) and rrt_max increase causing service degradation", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(paymentservice)", "observation": "pod_processes increased f